<bibRefCitation author="Lansdown, R. V." box="[493,725,446,472]" pageId="12" pageNumber="65" refId="ref15552" refString="Lansdown, R. V. (2008) Water starworts of Europe. BSBI Handbook No. 11. Botanical Society of the British Isles, London, 180 pp." type="book" year="2008">Lansdown [2008: 24</bibRefCitation>
(6–6x), 81, 83] and in 
<bibRefCitation author="Lansdown, R. V." box="[983,1176,446,472]" pageId="12" pageNumber="65" pagination="243 - 284" refId="ref15440" refString="Lansdown, R. V. (2022) The genus Callitriche (Plantaginaceae, Callitricheae) in Australasia and Oceania. Phytotaxa 547 (3): 243 - 284." type="journal article" year="2022">Lansdown (2022</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 10j).
</paragraph>
